original_title: コンビニバイト先に埋もれていた訳ありJカップお姉さんと昼夜問わずヤリまくる毎日。 安齋らら
overview: This guy begins to work at a convenience store and meets with Rion. A beautiful lady with an insanely hot body, that strangely enough doesn’t do any work as a cashier.  One day they go out drinking together and he learns about her dark past and traumas. He gets to understand everything, but that doesn’t discourage him… from his banging Rion plans.
title: I Fuck The J-Cup Girl With A Dark Past Who Works At The Convenience Store Every Day.Rara Anzai
